00:00:52.218 --> 00:00:53.620 align:start size:31% position:69%
All right?

00:00:53.620 --> 00:00:55.555 size:88% position:56%
But there are certain things
that I struggle with that--

00:00:55.555 --> 00:00:59.892 align:end position:100%
