into our relationship too.

00:00:59.892 --> 00:01:01.727 align:end position:100%
So there's a lot of stuff
that goes around.

00:01:01.727 --> 00:01:03.396 align:end position:100%
I'm not that tyrant
all the time.

00:01:03.396 --> 00:01:05.397 align:start position:0%
Let me put this
in a different perspective.

00:01:05.397 --> 00:01:08.434 align:start position:0%
There are absolutely
two sides to your stories.

00:01:08.434 --> 00:01:10.136 align:start position:0%
You have a side;
she has a side.

00:01:10.136 --> 00:01:11.170 align:start position:0%
But it's just not okay

00:01:11.170 --> 00:01:13.406 align:start position:0%
