to express herself

00:01:13.406 --> 00:01:15.240
and have to just eat that up.

00:01:15.240 --> 00:01:17.243 align:start position:0%
It's not okay for you
to attack her character.

00:01:17.243 --> 00:01:20.847 align:end position:100%
And I'm--I want
to live my life.

00:01:20.847 --> 00:01:22.148 align:start size:59% position:41%
I want to be happy,

00:01:22.148 --> 00:01:25.452 align:end position:100%
and I want my kids
to be happy.

00:01:27.921 --> 00:01:29.589 align:end position:100%
I need you to do
something for him,

00:01:29.589 --> 00:01:33.759 align:start size:78% position:22%
'cause I think he's open.

00:01:33.759 --> 00:01:34.794 align:end position:100%
I need you
to look at him

00:01:34.794 --> 00:01:37.797 align:end position:100%
and tell him if you're
really done.

00:01:37.797 --> 00:01:40.933 size:78% position:39%
Just look at him and say
whatever you need to say,

00:01:40.933 --> 00:01:42.769 size:88% position:44%
because he needs to hear it.

00:01:47.874 --> 00:01:49.642 align:end position:100%
We've been together
for a long time,

00:01:49.642 --> 00:01:51.043 align:start size:41% position:59%
for 13 years.

00:01:51.043 --> 00:01:53.612 align:end position:100%
We've been through--
we have two beautiful children.

00:01:53.612 --> 00:01:56.115 align:end position:100%
I love them
with all my heart.

00:01:56.115 --> 00:01:58.284
- I know you love them too.
- Yeah.

00:01:58.284 --> 00:02:00.653 align:end position:100%
As much as I've
been at peace

00:02:00.653 --> 00:02:02.789 align:end position:100%
and as much--
I want that with us.

00:02:02.789 --> 00:02:05.224 align:start position:0%
Right.

00:02:05.224 --> 00:02:07.827 align:end position:100%
But I don't want--
I don't want to be hurt.

00:02:07.827 --> 00:02:10.630 align:end position:100%
I don't want you
to hurt the kids.

00:02:12.798 --> 00:02:14.167 align:start position:0%
(Colby)
I'm all yours.

00:02:14.167 --> 00:02:18.671 align:start position:0%
I mean, I will shut--
I'll keep my mouth shut gladly

00:02:18.671 --> 00:02:18.705 align:start position:0%
